        "authorId" : "cbc74313-e7e9-4313-b106-3e17fde5473d",
        "body" : "I see, it is `//`. It is kind of a misnomer if we ever start supporting `file://`",
        "createdAt" : "2021-05-19T18:14:33Z",
        "updatedAt" : "2021-05-19T18:14:33Z",
        "lastEditedBy" : "cbc74313-e7e9-4313-b106-3e17fde5473d",
        "tags" : [
